title: ESET Smart Security 8.0.312.0 [32bit-64bit] 2015
description:
ESET Smart Security is a security suite for your PC, including the following solutions: Anti-Virus, Anti-Spyware, Anti-Rootkit, Anti-Spam, Anti-Theft, Firewall, Parental Controls, Web and e-mail protection. ESET Smart Security is among the leaders in the virus, Trojan and spyware detection and removal. That is very fast and uses less system resources than most of its competitors. System Requirements: Windows 8.x, 7, Vista, Home Server:
1 GHz 32-bit (x86) or 64-bit (x64) processor
512 MB (1 GB for Vista x64) RAM of system memory
320 MB available space

Windows XP Service Pack 3:
400 MHz 32-bit (x86)/ 64-bit (x64) processor
128 MB RAM of system memory
320 MB available disk space
